    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="752783612">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-752783612" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-752783612" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="752783612">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kevingchan/">玛格丽特*YEAR</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-05-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">把城市当做一个有生命的个体，从生长的角度去观察一座城市的诞生到衰亡，这样的角度让复杂和枯燥的事情变得生动而有趣了。像看故事一样的读完它，感觉对城市有了很多新的认识。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="737885603">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
